Just noting that we get the externalPath from the @PathParam so adding the host and context back on is why I added the toDomain() method to the HttpIdentifierConverter. So these two lines could be
final String fedoraId = identifierConverter().toInternalId(identifierConverter().toDomain(externalPath()));

Otherwise we could remove the externalPath() setup and make either externalUri and/or fedoraId into a class variable as this will probably be needed.

